[DETAILED LOGIC FLOW]

The `FragmentManagerKt` class defines several static extension methods for `FragmentManager`, each designed to simplify `FragmentTransaction` handling:

1.  **`commit(FragmentManager fragmentManager, boolean z2, l<? super FragmentTransaction, j> lVar)`**:
